&nbsp;There&nbsp;was&nbsp;something very warm&nbsp;about&nbsp;don Juan's&nbsp;house. I&nbsp;preferred that&nbsp;scene.<br>&nbsp;I&nbsp;next&nbsp;had&nbsp;a&nbsp;terrifying&nbsp;seizure,&nbsp;so&nbsp;shocking&nbsp;that&nbsp;my&nbsp;entire&nbsp;ordinary&nbsp;awareness&nbsp;came&nbsp;back&nbsp;to&nbsp;<br>
