happened.&nbsp;He&nbsp;gave&nbsp;me&nbsp;some&nbsp;food&nbsp;and&nbsp;said&nbsp;that&nbsp;I&nbsp;had&nbsp;to&nbsp;eat&nbsp;a&nbsp;great&nbsp;deal&nbsp;to&nbsp;compensate&nbsp;for&nbsp;my&nbsp;<br>expenditure&nbsp;of&nbsp;energy.<br>
