<i>power</i>&nbsp;to enable&nbsp;you to turn your&nbsp;<i>will&nbsp;</i>into a&nbsp;functioning unit.&quot;<br>
<i>Will&nbsp;</i>was&nbsp;another&nbsp;concept&nbsp;which&nbsp;don&nbsp;Juan&nbsp;had&nbsp;delineated&nbsp;with&nbsp;great&nbsp;care&nbsp;but&nbsp;without&nbsp;making&nbsp;it&nbsp;<br>
