I&nbsp;remarked&nbsp;to&nbsp;don&nbsp;Juan&nbsp;that&nbsp;there&nbsp;was&nbsp;no&nbsp;chance&nbsp;that&nbsp;anything&nbsp;so&nbsp;vague&nbsp;could&nbsp;ever&nbsp;be&nbsp;a&nbsp;<br>
functioning unit&nbsp;in my life.<br>
