I&nbsp;experienced an overwhelming apprehension.<br>&quot;Is&nbsp;all&nbsp;this&nbsp;necessary?&quot;&nbsp;I&nbsp;asked.<br>&quot;It's&nbsp;Genaro's&nbsp;request&nbsp;and must&nbsp;be&nbsp;obeyed,&quot;&nbsp;he&nbsp;said in a&nbsp;firm&nbsp;but&nbsp;friendly tone.<br>&quot;But&nbsp;what&nbsp;does&nbsp;don Genaro have&nbsp;to do with me?&quot;<br>&quot;You may find that&nbsp;out&nbsp;today,&quot;&nbsp;he&nbsp;said and smiled.<br>I&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pleaded&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;with&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;don&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Juan&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;to&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;get&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;me&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;out&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;of&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;that&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;intolerable&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;situation&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;explain&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;all&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the&nbsp;<br>
47<br>
<hr>
<A name=48></a>mysterious&nbsp;talk.&nbsp;He&nbsp;laughed&nbsp;and&nbsp;patted&nbsp;my&nbsp;chest&nbsp;and&nbsp;made&nbsp;a&nbsp;joke&nbsp;about&nbsp;a&nbsp;Mexican&nbsp;weight&nbsp;lifter&nbsp;<br>who&nbsp;had&nbsp;enormous&nbsp;pectoral&nbsp;muscles&nbsp;but&nbsp;could&nbsp;not&nbsp;do&nbsp;heavy&nbsp;physical&nbsp;labor&nbsp;because&nbsp;his&nbsp;back&nbsp;was&nbsp;<br>weak.<br>
