<A name=54></a>you&nbsp;arrived&nbsp;and&nbsp;I&nbsp;knew&nbsp;that&nbsp;I&nbsp;had&nbsp;to&nbsp;call&nbsp;Genaro&nbsp;so&nbsp;he&nbsp;could&nbsp;explain&nbsp;to&nbsp;you&nbsp;the&nbsp;mystery&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;<br>dreamer&nbsp;and the&nbsp;dreamed. You believed then, just&nbsp;as&nbsp;you always&nbsp;have, that&nbsp;I&nbsp;was&nbsp;tricking you;&nbsp;but&nbsp;<br>Genaro&nbsp;was&nbsp;not&nbsp;hiding&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;bushes&nbsp;as&nbsp;you&nbsp;thought.&nbsp;He&nbsp;came&nbsp;over&nbsp;for&nbsp;you,&nbsp;even&nbsp;if&nbsp;your&nbsp;reason&nbsp;<br>refuses&nbsp;to believe&nbsp;it.&quot;<br>
&nbsp;That&nbsp;part&nbsp;of&nbsp;don&nbsp;Juan's&nbsp;elucidation&nbsp;was&nbsp;indeed&nbsp;the&nbsp;hardest&nbsp;to&nbsp;take&nbsp;at&nbsp;its&nbsp;face&nbsp;value.&nbsp;I&nbsp;could&nbsp;not&nbsp;<br>
admit&nbsp;it. I&nbsp;said that&nbsp;don Genaro had been real&nbsp;and of&nbsp;this&nbsp;world.<br>
&quot;Everything&nbsp;that&nbsp;you've&nbsp;witnessed&nbsp;so&nbsp;far&nbsp;has&nbsp;been&nbsp;real&nbsp;and&nbsp;of&nbsp;this&nbsp;world,&quot;&nbsp;he&nbsp;said.&nbsp;&quot;There&nbsp;is&nbsp;no&nbsp;<br>
other&nbsp;world.&nbsp;Your&nbsp;stumbling&nbsp;block&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;peculiar&nbsp;insistence&nbsp;on&nbsp;your&nbsp;part&nbsp;and&nbsp;that&nbsp;peculiarity&nbsp;of&nbsp;<br>yours&nbsp;is&nbsp;not&nbsp;going&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;cured&nbsp;by&nbsp;explanations.&nbsp;So&nbsp;today&nbsp;Genaro&nbsp;addressed&nbsp;himself&nbsp;directly&nbsp;to&nbsp;<br>your&nbsp;body.&nbsp;A&nbsp;careful&nbsp;examination&nbsp;of&nbsp;what&nbsp;you&nbsp;did&nbsp;today&nbsp;will&nbsp;reveal&nbsp;to&nbsp;you&nbsp;that&nbsp;your&nbsp;body&nbsp;put&nbsp;<br>things&nbsp;together&nbsp;in&nbsp;a&nbsp;most&nbsp;praiseworthy&nbsp;manner.&nbsp;Somehow,&nbsp;you&nbsp;refrained&nbsp;from&nbsp;indulging&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;<br>visions&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;irrigation&nbsp;ditch.&nbsp;You&nbsp;kept&nbsp;a&nbsp;rare&nbsp;control&nbsp;and&nbsp;aloofness&nbsp;as&nbsp;warriors&nbsp;should;&nbsp;you&nbsp;didn't&nbsp;<br>believe&nbsp;anything,&nbsp;but&nbsp;you&nbsp;still&nbsp;acted&nbsp;efficiently&nbsp;and&nbsp;thus&nbsp;you&nbsp;were&nbsp;capable&nbsp;of&nbsp;following&nbsp;Genaro's&nbsp;<br>call. You actually found him&nbsp;without&nbsp;any aid from&nbsp;me.<br>
