We&nbsp;were&nbsp;silent&nbsp;for&nbsp;a&nbsp;few&nbsp;minutes.&nbsp;I&nbsp;waited&nbsp;for&nbsp;him&nbsp;to&nbsp;speak.&nbsp;Finally&nbsp;I&nbsp;asked,&nbsp;&quot;Did&nbsp;don&nbsp;Genaro&nbsp;<br>
make&nbsp;me&nbsp;leap up to the&nbsp;rock ledge?&quot;<br>
&quot;Don't&nbsp;take&nbsp;that&nbsp;leap&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;sense&nbsp;that&nbsp;you&nbsp;understand&nbsp;a&nbsp;leap,&quot;&nbsp;he&nbsp;said.&nbsp;&quot;Once&nbsp;again,&nbsp;this&nbsp;is&nbsp;only&nbsp;<br>
