&quot;What&nbsp;was&nbsp;there&nbsp;in that&nbsp;scene, don Juan?&nbsp;What&nbsp;was&nbsp;so important?&quot;<br>&quot;I&nbsp;don't&nbsp;know. It&nbsp;wasn't&nbsp;happening to me.&quot;<br>&quot;What&nbsp;do you mean?&quot;<br>
