&quot;For&nbsp;the&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>nagual,&nbsp;&nbsp;</i>it's&nbsp;nothing&nbsp;to&nbsp;move&nbsp;the&nbsp;way&nbsp;you&nbsp;did&nbsp;this&nbsp;morning.&nbsp;Especially&nbsp;for&nbsp;your&nbsp;<br>
