Hours&nbsp;later,&nbsp;after&nbsp;eating&nbsp;lunch&nbsp;and&nbsp;resting,&nbsp;don&nbsp;Juan&nbsp;and&nbsp;I&nbsp;sat&nbsp;on&nbsp;his&nbsp;favorite&nbsp;bench&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;park&nbsp;<br>
