I&nbsp;told&nbsp;him&nbsp;that&nbsp;my&nbsp;reaction&nbsp;began&nbsp;when&nbsp;he&nbsp;had&nbsp;asked&nbsp;me&nbsp;if&nbsp;I&nbsp;could&nbsp;feel&nbsp;what&nbsp;my&nbsp;<i>nagual</i>&nbsp;had&nbsp;<br>
