I&nbsp;wanted him&nbsp;to explain that&nbsp;idea. He&nbsp;laughed and raised an accusing finger&nbsp;at&nbsp;me.<br>&quot;This&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;recapitulation,&quot;&nbsp;he&nbsp;said. &quot;We'll&nbsp;get&nbsp;to that&nbsp;later.&quot;<br>He&nbsp;&nbsp;asserted&nbsp;&nbsp;that&nbsp;&nbsp;because&nbsp;&nbsp;of&nbsp;&nbsp;his&nbsp;&nbsp;decoy&nbsp;maneuver&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I&nbsp;&nbsp;became&nbsp;&nbsp;interested&nbsp;in&nbsp;&nbsp;erasing&nbsp;&nbsp;personal&nbsp;<br>
history&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>dreaming</i>.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;He&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;said&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;that&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;effects&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;of&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;those&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;two&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;techniques&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;were&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ultimately&nbsp;<br>devastating&nbsp;if&nbsp;they&nbsp;were&nbsp;exercised&nbsp;in&nbsp;their&nbsp;totality,&nbsp;and&nbsp;that&nbsp;then&nbsp;his&nbsp;concern&nbsp;was&nbsp;the&nbsp;concern&nbsp;of&nbsp;<br>every&nbsp;teacher,&nbsp;not&nbsp;to&nbsp;let&nbsp;his&nbsp;apprentice&nbsp;do&nbsp;anything&nbsp;that&nbsp;would&nbsp;plunge&nbsp;him&nbsp;into&nbsp;aberration&nbsp;and&nbsp;<br>morbidity.<br>
&quot;Erasing&nbsp;personal&nbsp;history&nbsp;and&nbsp;<i>dreaming&nbsp;</i>should&nbsp;only&nbsp;be&nbsp;a&nbsp;help,&quot;&nbsp;he&nbsp;said.&nbsp;&quot;What&nbsp;any&nbsp;apprentice&nbsp;<br>
needs&nbsp;to&nbsp;buffer&nbsp;him&nbsp;is&nbsp;temperance&nbsp;and&nbsp;strength.&nbsp;That's&nbsp;why&nbsp;a&nbsp;teacher&nbsp;introduces&nbsp;the&nbsp;warrior's&nbsp;<br>way,&nbsp;or&nbsp;living&nbsp;like&nbsp;a&nbsp;warrior.&nbsp;This&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;glue&nbsp;that&nbsp;joins&nbsp;together&nbsp;everything&nbsp;in&nbsp;a&nbsp;sorcerer's&nbsp;world.&nbsp;<br>Bit&nbsp;by&nbsp;bit&nbsp;a&nbsp;teacher&nbsp;must&nbsp;forge&nbsp;and&nbsp;develop&nbsp;it.&nbsp;Without&nbsp;the&nbsp;sturdiness&nbsp;and&nbsp;level-headedness&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;<br>warrior's&nbsp;way there&nbsp;is&nbsp;no possibility of&nbsp;withstanding the&nbsp;path of&nbsp;knowledge.&quot;<br>
