<A name=157></a>&quot;It&nbsp;means&nbsp;that&nbsp;the&nbsp;warrior&nbsp;has&nbsp;finally&nbsp;encountered&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>power</i>,&quot;&nbsp;don&nbsp;Juan&nbsp;said.&nbsp;&quot;No&nbsp;one&nbsp;can&nbsp;tell&nbsp;<br>
what&nbsp;each&nbsp;warrior&nbsp;would&nbsp;do&nbsp;with&nbsp;it;&nbsp;perhaps&nbsp;you&nbsp;two&nbsp;will&nbsp;roam&nbsp;peacefully&nbsp;and&nbsp;unnoticed&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;<br>face&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;earth, or&nbsp;perhaps&nbsp;you will&nbsp;turn out&nbsp;to be&nbsp;hateful&nbsp;men, or&nbsp;perhaps&nbsp;notorious, or&nbsp;kind. All&nbsp;<br>that&nbsp;depends&nbsp;on the&nbsp;impeccability and the&nbsp;freedom&nbsp;of&nbsp;your&nbsp;spirit.<br>
&quot;The&nbsp;important&nbsp;thing,&nbsp;however,&nbsp;is&nbsp;your&nbsp;task.&nbsp;That&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;bestowal&nbsp;made&nbsp;by&nbsp;a&nbsp;teacher&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;<br>
benefactor&nbsp;to&nbsp;their&nbsp;apprentices.&nbsp;I&nbsp;pray&nbsp;that&nbsp;you&nbsp;two&nbsp;will&nbsp;succeed&nbsp;in&nbsp;bringing&nbsp;your&nbsp;tasks&nbsp;to&nbsp;a&nbsp;<br>culmination.&quot;<br>
