There&nbsp;was&nbsp;a&nbsp;mild&nbsp;slope&nbsp;down&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;bottom&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;land&nbsp;formation,&nbsp;then&nbsp;there&nbsp;was&nbsp;a&nbsp;narrow&nbsp;flat&nbsp;<br>
