&quot;Right&nbsp;where&nbsp;that&nbsp;ditch is, there&nbsp;was&nbsp;a&nbsp;row&nbsp;of&nbsp;trees&nbsp;on the&nbsp;mountain in the&nbsp;story,&quot;&nbsp;he&nbsp;said.&nbsp;<br>
&quot;Beyond that&nbsp;point&nbsp;there&nbsp;was&nbsp;a&nbsp;thick forest.<br>
