walking&nbsp;down&nbsp;the&nbsp;slope&nbsp;towards&nbsp;the&nbsp;trees.&nbsp;His&nbsp;comrades&nbsp;then&nbsp;cocked&nbsp;their&nbsp;weapons&nbsp;and&nbsp;aimed&nbsp;at&nbsp;<br>him.&nbsp;If&nbsp;no&nbsp;one&nbsp;shot,&nbsp;or&nbsp;if&nbsp;the&nbsp;warrior&nbsp;survived&nbsp;his&nbsp;wounds&nbsp;and&nbsp;reached&nbsp;the&nbsp;edge&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;trees,&nbsp;he&nbsp;<br>was&nbsp;free.&quot;<br>
We&nbsp;went&nbsp;back to the&nbsp;place&nbsp;where&nbsp;we&nbsp;had been sitting.<br>&quot;How&nbsp;about&nbsp;now, witness?&quot;&nbsp;he&nbsp;asked Nestor. &quot;Can you tell?&quot;<br>Nestor&nbsp;was&nbsp;the&nbsp;epitome&nbsp;of&nbsp;nervousness.&nbsp;He&nbsp;took&nbsp;off&nbsp;his&nbsp;hat&nbsp;and&nbsp;scratched&nbsp;his&nbsp;head.&nbsp;He&nbsp;then&nbsp;<br>
