everybody else.<br>
&quot;They&nbsp;say&nbsp;that&nbsp;there&nbsp;were&nbsp;men&nbsp;who&nbsp;pulled&nbsp;through&nbsp;unharmed,&quot;&nbsp;don&nbsp;Genaro&nbsp;continued.&nbsp;&quot;Let's&nbsp;<br>
