Don Genaro looked at&nbsp;me&nbsp;and then at&nbsp;Pablito.<br>&quot;There&nbsp;was&nbsp;a&nbsp;condition&nbsp;set&nbsp;up&nbsp;for&nbsp;that&nbsp;walk&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;edge&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;trees,&quot;&nbsp;he&nbsp;went&nbsp;on.&nbsp;&quot;The&nbsp;warrior&nbsp;<br>
